\f2\b\fs32 Flare fittings
\f1\b0  consist of a body with a flared or coned end. Special flaring tools are used to create a matching flare on the pipe.  The flare nut compresses the flare into the fitting body and creates the seal. Flare fittings\'a0can handle higher pressures and a wider range of operating parameters than standard compression fittings.\
